<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="296" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1451,1990,2089]" pageId="0" pageNumber="296">
Two syntypes collections (
<emphasis box="[430,567,1990,2016]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="296">Kotschy 568</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[618,760,1990,2017]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="296">Aucher 5158</emphasis>
) were cited in 
<bibRefCitation author="Bentham, G." box="[921,1101,1990,2016]" editor="Candolle, A. P. de" journalOrPublisher="Treuttel et Wurtz, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="297" pagination="27 - 603" part="12" refString="Bentham, G. (1848) Labiatae. In: Candolle, A. P. de (Ed.) Prodromus Systematis Naturalis Regni Vegetabilis, vol. 12. Treuttel et Wurtz, Paris, pp. 27 - 603." title="Labiatae" type="journal article" volumeTitle="Prodromus Systematis Naturalis Regni Vegetabilis" year="1848">Bentham (1848)</bibRefCitation>
protologue for 
<taxonomicName box="[1271,1451,1990,2017]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Scutellaria" kingdom="Fungi" order="Lamiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="296" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glechomoides">
<emphasis box="[1271,1451,1990,2017]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="296">S. glechomoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and both are now deposited at K. The sheet 
<emphasis box="[619,758,2026,2052]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="296">Kotschy 568</emphasis>
is selected as lectotype because its leaves, flowers, bracts, and inflorescence are more developed than the other sheet, matching clearly the characters mentioned in the protologue.
</paragraph>
